l,"customfield_10306":null,"customfield_10702":null,"customfield_10703":null,"customfield_10308":null,"resolutiondate":"2013-05-17T10:49:00.971-0500","customfield_10704":null,"customfield_10309":[{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/customFieldOption/10204","value":"KVM","id":"10204"}],"customfield_10705":null,"workratio":-1,"lastViewed":null,"watches":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/EUCA-5366/watchers","watchCount":5,"isWatching":false},"created":"2013-03-13T05:40:53.274-0500","customfield_12000":null,"priority":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/priority/3","iconUrl":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/images/icons/priorities/major.svg","name":"Major","id":"3"},"customfield_12400":null,"customfield_12201":null,"customfield_12600":"{}","customfield_10300":null,"customfield_10102":null,"labels":["3.4-PM"],"customfield_10301":null,"customfield_11700":null,"timeestimate":null,"aggregatetimeoriginalestimate":null,"versions":[],"customfield_11901":null,"issuelinks":[],"assignee":null,"updated":"2013-05-17T10:49:01.002-0500","status":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/status/6","description":"The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are closed can be reopened.","iconUrl":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/images/icons/statuses/generic.png","name":"Closed","id":"6","statusCategory":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/statuscategory/3","id":3,"key":"done","colorName":"green","name":"Done"}},"components":[{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/component/10010","id":"10010","name":"Node Controller"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/component/11300","id":"11300","name":"QA","description":"Bugs/Tasks associated with the QA team"}],"timeoriginalestimate":null,"customfield_13000":null,"description":"Hi,\r\n\r\nI'm using faststart to establish private cloud. I have installed windows 7 image into it. When I try to run the windows 7 instance and access it from client machine(windows xp) I'm able to log on to it. It works very well for hours! Now when I attach a volume using \"euca-attach-volume  vol-BC8B3F3E  i-F79841A6 -d /dev/sde\" it gets attached. I could also see the volume attached from the remote desktop. But after 5 mins the remote desktop connection gets disconneted. Then even if I try to remote desktop to that instance it does not get connected. Still the status of instance is running and volume is attached.\r\n\r\nThen I executed \"netstat -tulpn | grep kvm\" command on NC and got the port number of the running instance. Then I used the VNC viewer from the windows xp machine to logon to the running instance. I used<ip-of-NC>:<port-no-of-instance> to logon to it it. It showed up that its connecting but then it simply blinked and then nothing happened. Tried it from different XP machines with VNC viewer, still the same result. Then I used a machine running CentOS 6.3 and from that using \"Remote Desktop Viewer\" I did the same thing ie. used<ip-of-NC>:<port-no-of-instance> and I was surprised to see that it opened up. I was able to log on to that instance from this machine. I could also see the volune attached to it. Worked very well. But now I'm not able to understancd why it did not open from VNC Viewer in windows XP? And why is the connection getting disconnected when I'm using RDP from windows XP or windows 7 machine? Is there any settings in windows OS to be configured so as to make it alive all time?\r\n\r\n\r\nFor your reference here are the links of a video showing the error, cc.log,nc.log and libvirt.xsl:\r\n\r\nhttps://www.dropbox.com/s/xc1dgwlzw7ilzz0/video-2013-03-05-17-00-13.mp4\r\nhttps://www.dropbox.com/s/v3niacwzc0ath0r/new_cc.log\r\nhttps://www.dropbox.com/s/6m1km7ksep80mnf/new_nc.log\r\nhttps://www.dropbox.com/s/sbngmkxsp0epegh/libvirt.xsl\r\n\r\nPlz help me in this issue.\r\n\r\nThanking you in anticipation,\r\nRegards,\r\nRadhakrishnan","customfield_13200":null,"customfield_11300":"PRD-16","customfield_11500":null,"timetracking":{},"customfield_10005":null,"customfield_10401":null,"customfield_10600":null,"customfield_12900":null,"attachment":[],"aggregatetimeestimate":null,"summary":"Unable to remote desktop to windows 7 instance after volume attachment","creator":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=rk","name":"rk","key":"rk","accountId":"557058:c361950b-7c53-47bd-a5fc-6ae94b148aea","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a492cc38d3ff8072ce8cad3c4db9d1ac?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a492cc38d3ff8072ce8cad3c4db9d1ac?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a492cc38d3ff8072ce8cad3c4db9d1ac?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a492cc38d3ff8072ce8cad3c4db9d1ac?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Radhakrishnan S. Iyer","active":false,"timeZone":"Asia/Kolkata"},"subtasks":[],"reporter":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=rk","name":"rk","key":"rk","accountId":"557058:c361950b-7c53-47bd-a5fc-6ae94b148aea","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a492cc38d3ff8072ce8cad3c4db9d1ac?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a492cc38d3ff8072ce8cad3c4db9d1ac?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a492cc38d3ff8072ce8cad3c4db9d1ac?s=16&d=https